        <updateDate>2005-04-04T14:49:25Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Small Business Expensing Permanency Act of 2005 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to make permanent the increased expensing allowance ($100,000) for depreciable business assets and related provisions pertaining to phaseout amounts, inflation adjustments, and the period for revocation of an election.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
